{
  "stem": "4226.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Can you repeat it, please?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was a full load from, from the--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--brick factory right through.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, about [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] about one night and part of two days.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No food.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we arrived there, former prisoners opened the doors, who were working for--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jewish, in striped uniform.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And everyone had to get off the train, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] lined up five in a row, male separately, and females separately, and go to a selection table.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And a German officer was looking at everybody and having a small stick, about-- could be 18 inches.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was waving right or left.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Those who were fit to work, he signaled to go to the right.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the same system was another officer at another table for the women.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So...",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Our own clothes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother was quite young.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was 42.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she was sent to the left, because she kept-- [PAUSES FOR 26 SECONDS] [CRYING] she kept the small child of someone else.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was a good friend-- she was a good friend of hers, district doctor's wife.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this doctor himself was from Czech territory, Hungarian-attached Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was doing sort of a military service and appointed to our village, and to seven villages as a-- as a doctor.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The small one could have been, her mother held, about a year and a half.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she had another one two and a half, and another one three and a half or four, three kids.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the Germans didn't separate mothers from babies or children.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So even if she would have fitted for work, if she had someone else's child, they would send her to the left.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
